It would be great to be able to display a tag cloud which only shows the most popular tags of a certain period. The user should be able to define this period, e.g. to only include the most popular labels of the last 30 days.

If the labels in a Wiki don't change very often, the tag cloud (using the popular-label macro) becomes a bit boring after a while, due to the fact that the labels of the tag cloud only slightly change.

